HEADWORD: Bandrol
<hw>Band"rol</hw> }</mhw>
<pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F. <ets>banderole</ets>, dim. of
<ets>bandi⟦egrave⟧re</ets>, <ets>banni⟦egrave⟧re</ets>, banner; cf. It.
