<def>A little banner, flag, or streamer.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>bannerol</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>From the extremity of which fluttered a small <qex>banderole</qex>
